So basically... I decided to start using this thing...AGAIN. lol. Let's Talk About My Weekend...
Friday
School was usual. At 7, Me, Nick, Dottie, Ali, and Ec... met up with Nina, Pom and Brandon and Mrs. Brown and Mrs. Sclater at Jmoneys last homegame. Afterwards, All of us plus Jmoney and Minus Mrs. Brown and Sclater went to Applebees. We saw Jamal Prather there... it was weird. lol. After that Me, Ali, Amber, Jmoney and Nick went off roading in the element... Me, Ali and Nick were in the backseat when Jmoney went over some tracks at 80 MPH... well lets see... i almost broke my jaw... Ali's "12 pound head" (as Nick calls it) hit nicks rib cage full force, and Ali's Neck was hurting. So then we dropped everyone off and I came home. Like 20 minutes later, I IMed Nick to see if his chest was okay and we both decided we were bored as hell and that he was going to come over and watch a movie. When he got here it was about 1 am... and we decided to watch "Sweet Home Alabama"... Then his ass decided he was hungry and so I made him a Ham and Cheese Sandwich and We both ended up falling asleep.
Saturday
Woke up at around 10:30 and decided to make breakfast for me and lil grey boy. lol. So I Made cinnomon rolls and Ali came over. After we ate... we came upstairs and nick checked his myspace and Me and Ali just talked. Then Nick decided the pack of gum I found on my floor was his... so then we faught and well.. i moreless got my ass whooped because he is strong as hell. lol. Then him and Ali went home. I then layed around for a little while, got ready, Jmoney came over, and then we went to pick Nick up from work. After that... I dropped him off... and Jmoney came over for a little bit, then left. I then hear a big BOOM and I look out my window and hear someone running... Someone egged my house. BIG MISTAKE. I have an idea... but im sure i will find out.. and when i do.. there ass is mine. However, after that... Jmoney and Me went and picked up Nick and we went to Tim Hortons for an Ice Capp, and Meijers. At Meijers... Me and Nick were reading Magazines while Jmoney decided she would read us and the whole store Dr. Suess. Lol. When we left there... We dropped Nick Off at Benavides house where Heather and everyone was gettin Crunk at.(Thanks Jes for inviting me by the way.) After we dropped him off... Jmoney dropped me off...and I passed out. lol.
Sunday
Today...Dottie and Jmoney came over for a little bit. We watched the "Gilmore Girl" Marathon.. and ate IMOAN fried chicken. Then they left... and Nay Nay and my Aunt Sally came over for a bit. Then Ali out of no where at 11 comes busting thru my door with an orange cone and left. LMAO. It was amusing. Then I talked to her on the phone for a lil bit and here I am now... I'm going to bed now... Until tomorrow...<3

Wow. So since July... ALOT has changed. I quit both jobs.. it was just too much, and too little money. I now get along with Amy. My hair is Blonde! Me and Ralph arent half as close, since he began dating Arlesia(Not saying its her fault.) Paul completely broke my heart. TWICE. He does not care at all for me. I am finally getting over it. School is great. Love being a senior! Idk... everything is going good... for now..lol.

Good morning loves...

Yesterday was alright i suppose. I babysat from like 11 to 1030...long day! Then i went home... called PAUL!<3, we talked for a while... he made of me being so "white", and i made fun of him being "grey"...it was a good convo. Then ali's stupid ass assumes i am talking about her on my away message and TRIES to hoe me out... ignorant...I Then called heather, we talked for a bit, cuz welp... shes the greatest! lol. Then i fall asleep and raphael calls me and tells me he's leavin saturday morning to go up north for a month, and that hes been trying to get ahold of me so we can hang out before he goes. I'm gonna miss my best friend! ::tear::

Today I woke up... in a rather good mood may i add, got dressed, picked ec up, and came to summer school. After i get out of here i plan on goin home for a bit, and then goin up to pauls work to visit him...then to work at KFC from 6-10...sucks! Then i am sure i will call paul and get my goodnights from him and go to bed.

Tomorrow, i plan on sleeping in... babysitting for crystal for a lil bit... then goin up to visit my beautiful boyfriend at work... come home chill for a bit, and prolly pickin up my boyfriend... coming back to my house and watching ladder 49... and then who knows...

Until tomorrow...<3

Hello my loves!  My life has been so great the last couple of weeks... Paul has much to do with it! I have gotten super close again with ali<3... and everything is goin so smooth. Summer school is good... i like the people and the work isnt half as hard as i thought it would be!

Yesterday was great! Romello's 1st birthday party was yesterday. Paul, Amber, Josh, Ec and Ali all went too! A bunch of people were there... It was nice to spend time with paul though.. he works so much! After that Paul had to go home cuz he promised his lil cousin he would hang out with him... so that was upsetting... but i understood. We then dropped amber, ec and josh off at Ec's and me and ali went for a ride... and then to 7-11 and Taco bell. Later on we stopped at my Jareds baseball game and talked with crystal and all of them for a bit. Ali had to be home by 10, so i dropped her off and i went over to crystals. She had me go get diapers and a pizza for her, and then i left there and went and picked my mom up at work at 12. When i got home, i called my wonderful boyfriend... we talked for bout 45 minutes, and then i went to bed.

Today my plans include leaving here... gettin something to eat..I'm STARVING!.. and then goin to babysit until 10 tonight! Great joy... not! Well i'm about to get goin, i'm bout to get out of class... so until tomorrow...<3

Paul...6/25

So this morning i wake up, and my mom tells me about the bombings in London. It was like a flashback to 9-11... idk it was weird how it impacted me. Anyhow... i picked up ms. ec... drove to summer school... and am now sitting her typing this to you. Today I plan on babysittin till like 2 so crystal can get her breaks fixed. Then I plan on driving my mother to work... goin to visit paul(we need to talk...) and then coming home and hanging out with ec and dottie! I then plan on calling my bestman(ralph) lol... and then calling my darling boyfriend... then off to bed... only to sleep in tomorrow... 

I'll update later and let you know just how on track on was with my prediction of my day...

Oh... everyone make sure u pray for the people who were hurt and killed in london... god... its so sad...

Until later...<3

Well, well, well... lots has been happening since the "amy asswhoopin"...lol. Everywhere i go now, i get called scrapper...lol. Umm.. I have been gettin super close with ralph(best friend!), I've harrassed a cart boy at meijers by sayin mean things over a megaphone with jmoney, dottie and ec. I discovered i have a new fear... FISHFLIES! (Jmoney threw them boys all over me!) E.C went to texas(torture!), Ali went to France and Spain(Even more torture!). My mom had a suprise party for her 50... i got blew back with dottie...(GREAT FUN!)umm... OHH!!!..I have been PAULS! girlfriend since the 25 of june... wonderful... (Smiles).
 I had a lil birthday thingy with my 9 closest friends...so dont go gettin bent out of shape for not gettin "invited"(Brandon!). Anyhow, Me, paul,ralph, josh, heather, jes B, jmoney,amber, ali and dottie all went to mongolian BBQ to eat and then bowling till 130... then to my house till 3! Paul got me two dozen pink daiseys for my birthday(MY FAVORITE!).. how cute! lol. What else has been up... ummm... I babysit on mondays and wednesdays from 8am to 10pm. I also work on tuesdays and thursdays from 11-4 at KfC! So hopefully the money will come pouring in...lol.  Also, My cell phone got cut off cuz i forgot to pay that..but believe it will be back on by this weekend! Its been hell without it! Well now i am in summer school...lol... i know. I have to take a math class in order to graduate! whatev.. no big deal... plus i've met some new people... they're so non rouge... so nice! lol.. Well i will try to update more... but until then.. <3

I'm A  LOSER! lol

Okay so... I am sittin in 2 hour talkin to jessica cantrell about ms. bramble. (Mind you amy sits kitty corner from me)So I say... "bramble fuckin plays favoritism...(cuz she was callin a bunch of peoples houses) Amy who i end up findin out planned to fight me that day, butts in and says " and who are you refering to?"... i look at her like shes crazy and simply say, "dont talk to me, member, i'll get suspended" (cuz she went to like 4 administators and teachers about me... just tryin to get me suspended)... she then says... "well then tell me who the FUCK ur referring to"... i then tell her quite loudly enough to stop the class and look..." BITCH dont try to boss up on me!". I then turn around and continue my convo with jessica. Next thing i know i see my stuff off my desk and on the ground... i turn to look and amy tips my desk! I go to get up and she pushes me back down. I then get up... tell ec to "HOLD MY MOTHER FUCKIN GLASSES" and out of no where bramble tackles me against the board, while ms. gibbs is holding amy. I got amy tryin to act hard and say "now what bitch" while bramble is telling me... "DONT DO IT SALLY!" I then decided i wasnt goin out like a punk and pushed ms. gibbs and bramble out of my way and it was then that i punched amy straight in the middle of her face... my most proudest punch!!! Amy then grabs my hair(pussy fighting!) and trips me... i fall on my back... she jumps on top of me... and slaps me... one good time... i'll admit, it was a good slap. But then it all ended for her right then and there. I wrapped her hair in a knot with my left hand, and punched her AT LEAST 25 times in her face with my right. Next thing i know, mrs. cannon is on top of me holding my left arm down while i am STILL punchin amy with my right...all i hear is " STOP SALLY...STOP SALLY"... finally seeing only mrs. cannon i snap out of it and get up. It's then that i see amy go after ec. I then try to go after amy again to help ec... cuz amy gave her the rick james bitchslap... but my best friend proved everyone wrong, when she started beatin the fuck out of amy herself!!!! So mrs. cannon escorts me out of the room and to the 2 floor office... i have people who left there class to see the fight slappin my hands and tellin me good job and shit. lol. Mrs. cannon then tells me that i punched her in her face... not knowing, i apologize and she says its okay. I go and sit in mr.morgans office and ms. pallagi(amys aunt/hall monitor) walks in and gives me a lil AHHGG sorda sound... i figure, i'm gonna get suspended anyways and look at her, flinch and say "what the fuck you looking at?"... she then walks out... long story short... Me and Ec got 5 days... amy got expelled... and i cant run for president...

Was it worth it... HELL YES!!! That has to be one of the proudest moments in my entire life... BOTTOM LINE!!! <3

So I beat amys ass, bottom line!!

Details later...

<3 sally

Okay, so i havent updated in a while... i am gonna start to tho. Well today I got off work.. which was just a bad day. Paula came in with her 20 something year old boyfriend, who she left home to live with... she dropped out and she just looks different. Its sad to see your childhood friend so different. So that really got to me... i feel i cant help her. Anyhow, i worked 7 hours today, i am gonna go to crystals in a bit cuz i got to babysit tomorrow till 3:30 so i figured i mine as well stay the night. I tried venting to amber on the phone but she either kept saying hold on or let me call you back. VERY FUSTRATING... like she doesnt want to listen or doesnt care to! Then E.C... people tell me whats shes saying... how she feels toward me... yet when i ask her she denies anything... bullshit! Well its getting late, and a shower before crystals would be fantastic, so until later...

<3 Sally

Okay so I havent really  updated in forever... sorry! Well lets see whats been up... ummmm, I work weekends at KFC cuz my grades are not doing to well...I am playin varsity volleyball... I am gaining more confidence... i hate amy sprinkle.... and am TRYIN and am slowy gettin over paul. So, tonight my mom is going to my cousins party at a club, meaning i have the house and the car to myself till oh, about 2 in the mornin! YAY! prolly wont do anything tho. But am sure to have fun, dotties staying the night... we will find some trouble to get ourselfs in to! lol. As for today... It was alright. actually it blowed till after school. Fourth hour i went to the office to talk to my counseler ms. baskerville, cuz she wants me to read my poem i wrote at the assembly for black history month. So i read it to the other counseler and she started crying...lol... i think it meant she liked it. lol. Then i ms. benford our principal had me come down to her office for a lecture, cuz amys bitch ass told her all this shit i didnt do, i didnt get in trouble tho! But i did start crying cuz i hate being made out to be the bad guy, and then my eyes were all red and swollen, and i see amy and she fuckin starts cheesin in my face, luckily i didnt hit her... ONLY becuz i am runnin her spot as president next year and cant get suspended. So then i start walkin to 5 hour, and i am one step from walkin in my class and the bell rings, ms.pallagi catches me and sends me to morgan for a hallsweep... cuz she dont like me cuz shes amys aunt. So then morgan owed me so he let me go... and i didnt end up gettin a detention... thank god. so then after school, raphael came over till like 530 and i dropped him off at his game afterwards. and tonight dot's stayin and ecs goin on a date with jay... so i am happy for ec and anzious to see what me and dot are gonna get ourselfs into. Until tomorrow...</3

Long time no update, well where to start? School started, I got my license(No Points!), I am working back at Kfc. Homecoming was great, did ambers hair.. i will post some homecoming pictures on here. The usual really, still likin paul... duh... lol. volleyballs coming up.. just A WHOLE bunch of stuff.. its been fun..

Well, today I woke up, and fed the girls. Then I got the dressed and ready...took a shower... got ready myself, scrunched my hair. Just called jes, and shes gonna go up to the park with me and the girls. I dk what ali is doing anymore.... so until later...

Well last night I ended up staying at amys, we talked about everything. It was real great to vent. So this morning, We woke up, bullshitted. Came home, i changed, we went back to her house, went to burger king for lunch... I got a chicken whopper meal... i was so stuffed. So then, we went to Sams club with her mom, they got a whole bunch of shit! lol. So then, I got dropped off, went and picked up my girls.. hannah and olivia... for you's that dont know, they are my neices. They came back here, I fed them, painted their toes and finger nails. Then Jessica B. needed to vent, so she asked me to run to 7-11 with her. So the girls stayed here with my mom and I ran up to 7-11 and got the girls some slurpees. Now they are pooped. So they are laying in my bed watching kim possible. Tomorrow, Me, Hannah and Olivia are meeting up with Jessica B. and her nephew Jakob, and Ali and her neice Micala. We are all gonna take the kids up to the park. That should be great fun! So I am looking forward to it. 

Oh, my drama... Thomas had me blocked... i dont believe I did anything wrong. So then he unblocks me, i get happy... but now he just wont talk to me. JUST FUCKING GRAND! Thomas, I dont understand why your pissed at me, so if u would at least tell me... that would be nice. Cuz its driving me insane that your not talking to me! Geez

So now I am talking to heather who just got back from tennessee! And Lisa, who says shes a loser... NO UR NOT DARLING!!! I <3 YOU! 

Well I am gonna watch Kim Possible and go to bed, so until tomorrow... <3 Sal

Well today, After Nina left, My mom came home. Nina came over to see if i had a wallet, but it was too thick so i just ended up giving her a ziplock! lol. Then my mom asked me to go to the store with her and take a ride. So after that we stopped at my Aunt Margies house, showed her my nose ring. Then My mom went and got gas. I asked her to stop my crystals(Who I consider my sister), so i could see my new nephew! Romello Addison Walker... Born July 12 @ 6lbs. 8ozs. 21 inches long. He has got to be the cutest thing I have ever seen. So beautiful! So after that, I came home, my mom made salmon Patties with mash potatoes, and Peas. I grubbed that shit son! lol. Then my Aunt Sally stopped by. I am supposed to be going to amys but IDK know if i am cuz she hasent called me back... So we shall see what the night brings us. Tomorrow I am Having my Nieces Hannah and Olivia come stay the night. I shall take pictures. Until 2morrow... <3

Where to start... I feel as though I am nothing but an advice giver to friends. I am the one they always come to when they have problems in a relationship, and I give them the best advice I can. But why do they come to me? I have never had a real serious relationship with a guy before. Who knows. Anyways, I feel like I can't like anyone anymore, without a friend liking them. I only like certain guys, guys with a good outlook, someone who I know will do well in the future. I am not one to judge the guy I like on all looks. EVen though it is a plus. However, It always comes down to be just being the friend, and my girls always getting the guys. I've always just shook it off, but I feel I just cant hold it in any longer. I liked Thomas, he's a great guy, a gentleman, and he speaks two words and you know he's going somewhere in the future. We had great conversations, convo's I looked forward to everyday. But then, I find out him and my BEST friend amber like eachother AGAIN... the 5th time! I always support my friends, and he's just a crush. So what's there to do? I get upset, emotionally wrecked. I feel betrayed, like it was my fault. Now things are somewhat normal between me and amber, I mean i still feel like I can't trust her with things. As for thomas, I realized that I had more then a crush, I had a real great friendship with him. A friendship which is now, not at all what it was. It's sorda just a big mess. So there's ONE. Now, I liked Paul also. I've always had feelings for that kid. He's a gentleman, and he's intellegent, just my type. Well, which friend is going to like this crush now? Ahhh... E.C., my BEST friend. Only she dont sneak about it, she flirts and talks and stuff in front of my face. Of course, out of us two, whos the guy to like... my friend, never sally! So I just let it go, always, and try to let it go. But you get the feelings to go away, and then you talk to the guy and all the feelings of you liking them come right back. I dont know about my friends, but I know I am not going after the guys for their car, money, looks...etc. I feel i needed to get this off my chest, the hurt I feel everytime I allow myself to like someone, and one of the two BEST friends I have like the guys I like. Just goes to show I always just get to be the Friend, and always the one to give advice... IDK... I just dont know about allowing myself to like someone again...
